Functional Requirements

    Support operations: +, -, *, /.
    Evaluate mathematical expression with operator precedence (parentheses > *// > +/-).
    Recursively break down the expression into sub-expressions.
    One pass string processing, no lists or extra data structures.
    O(n) time complexity.
    Handle and process an empty string, return empty output.
    Return the number if the string contains only a number.
    Raise errors for:
        Misplaced operators.
        Misplaced parentheses.
        Division by zero.

Edge Cases

    Empty string → empty output.
    Single number → return the number.
    Invalid expressions → raise error.